data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3 bed 1 bath home nestled on 4 acres of land, offering the perfect combination of serenity and functionality. This picturesque home boasts multiple outbuildings, including a spacious barn, creating endless possibilities for outdoor hobbies, storage, or even a workshop. There is a detached one car garage and also a bonus outbuilding with a window unit currently being used as a craft room. The acreage is fully enclosed by barbed wire fencing, providing a secure and safe environment for livestock and creating an ideal space for homesteading activities. This tastefully renovated home features brand new flooring throughout, which provides both durability and sophistication. The sleek laminate flooring in the kitchen, master bedroom and carpeting in 2 of the bedrooms adds a touch of contemporary elegance. New AC unit in 2023, new furnace 2024, metal roof aprox 5 years old, all water lines have been updated to pex from water heater throughout. Call today!
